name: Our Demons, Our Selves
description: Once you own this 11Second video of collaged stop-motion animation go to the center most point of your living space after 1:30AM (but only after you own it, don't cheat or you're a cheater) and turn off all the lights and watch this video 11 times in a row on loop.  Once you have done that stop the video on any still frame and examine it for 1 minute and 11 seconds, do that with 11 different times with 11 different stills.  After you finish the last still stop the video and say I Own You, Sucker.
